              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M13.5 4.5L6.5 11.5L2.5 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>Engineer berpengalaman &amp; tim QC yang ketat</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="trust-icon">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M13.5 4.5L6.5 11.5L2.5 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>After-sales support &amp; garansi penuh setiap produk</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="trust-icon">
